<h2 id="toc1"><span>Tabs</span></h2>
<p>To add tabs to your sandbox so you can have multiple drafts, use the following code:</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[tabview]]
[[tab Title 1]]
Text goes here. Pretend this is a draft.
[[/tab]]
[[tab Title 2]]
More text in another tab! You can add lots of tabs.
[[/tab]]
[[/tabview]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p>If done correctly, you should get something like this:</p>
